sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster<br/>Controller
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization<br/>Controller
    participant SecGen as SecretGenerator<br/>Controller
    participant FeatureAPI as Feature API
    participant Manifests as /opt/manifests/<br/>(Local Filesystem)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant OSMon as OpenShift Monitoring

    Note over Admin,OSMon: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Reconciliation

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
    DSCCtrl->>Manifests: Read kustomize overlays<br/>(filesystem)
    Manifests-->>DSCCtrl: Component manifests
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply component resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Resources created/updated
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update DSC status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Admin,OSMon: Flow 2: DSCInitialization - Monitoring Setup (Managed RHOAI)

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR
    K8sAPI-->>DSCICtrl: Watch notification
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Get addon secrets<br/>(PagerDuty, SMTP, DeadMansSnitch)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCICtrl: Secret values
    DSCICtrl->>Manifests: Read monitoring manifests<br/>(filesystem)
    Manifests-->>DSCICtrl: Prometheus/Alertmanager configs
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy Prometheus + Alertmanager<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Routes (reencrypt TLS)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    OSMon->>Prom: Scrape metrics<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Admin,OSMon: Flow 3: KServe Serverless Feature Setup

    DSCCtrl->>FeatureAPI: Enable KServe component<br/>(in-process call)
    FeatureAPI->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    FeatureAPI->>K8sAPI: Create KnativeServing CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    FeatureAPI->>K8sAPI: Create Istio Gateways<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    FeatureAPI->>K8sAPI: Create FeatureTracker CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Admin,OSMon: Flow 4: Secret Generation and OAuth

    K8sAPI-->>SecGen: Watch: annotated Secret created
    SecGen->>SecGen: Generate random secret value
    SecGen->>K8sAPI: Update Secret with generated value<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    SecGen->>K8sAPI: Create OAuthClient CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
